dct_title_s: Israel / compiled, drawn & printed by the Survey of Israel, January 1950, partly revised by the Survey of Israel, June 1959.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints, spot heights, form lines, and rock drawings. Map shows international boundaries, railways, four categories of roads, places of worship, wadi, wadi beds, places of worship, and antiquities. Also shows "Armistice demarcation line, Demilitarized zone boundary, Division line."
